libfetchxsrf
============

Automate CSRF token extraction and login on web forms with Rust.

libfetchxsrf is a lightweight, blocking HTTP client library designed to simplify the process of fetching CSRF (Cross-Site Request Forgery) tokens and performing form-based logins. It's built on top of reqwest, scraper, and url, and provides both high-level convenience functions and a customizable builder for advanced use.

  

